OL,3,COllie Watkins seeks inspiration from
OL,4,CPeter Withe's 1982 European Cup winner
OL,6,FOllie Watkins will seek inspiration
OL,7,Ffor next week's Europa League final
OL,8,Fagainst Freiburg by watching video
OL,9,Ffootage of Peter Withe's famous winner
OL,10,Ffor Aston Villa in the 1982 European
OL,11,FCup final.
OL,13,FWithe wrote himself into Villa
OL,14,Ffolklore by scoring the only goal in
OL,15,FRotterdam 44 years ago when the West
OL,16,FMidlands club last won major European
OL,17,Fhonours by beating Bayern Munich 1-0.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
