OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779034270
OL,3,COllie Watkins seeks inspiration from
OL,4,CPeter Withe's 1982 European Cup winner
OL,6,FVilla's last major trophy win was in
OL,7,Fthe 1996 League Cup and they will bid
OL,8,Fto end their 30-year wait against
OL,9,FBundesliga side Freiburg at Besiktas
OL,10,FPark in Istanbul on Wednesday.
OL,12,FWatkins said: "I haven't actually
OL,13,F(seen Withe's winner), but I'm going
OL,14,Fto. I'm going to look back at it in
OL,15,Fthese next few days before the final
OL,16,Fas inspiration.
OL,18,F"I think Peter Withe is a legend. He
OL,19,Fcame in (to Bodymoor Heath). I've met
OL,20,Fhim quite a few times. He came into
OL,21,Fthe training ground last week to watch.
OL,26,@tD@OOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779034270
OL,3,COllie Watkins seeks inspiration from
OL,4,CPeter Withe's 1982 European Cup winner
OL,6,F"It's amazing that he can do that and
OL,7,Fthat we can have a legend around the
OL,8,Fplace."
OL,10,FVilla booked their place in the final
OL,11,Fwith a 4-1 aggregate win over
OL,12,FNottingham Forest in the last four.
OL,14,FUnai Emery's side then halted a run of
OL,15,Fone win in five league games to
OL,16,Ffinally seal Champions League
OL,17,Fqualification by beating Liverpool 4-2
OL,18,Fon Friday night and Watkins feels
OL,19,FVilla can now fully focus on the
OL,20,FEuropa League final.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
