OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779034270
OL,3,COllie Watkins seeks inspiration from
OL,4,CPeter Withe's 1982 European Cup winner
OL,6,F"For the last couple of league games
OL,7,Fit's been hard to focus because we've
OL,8,Fhad such highs (in the Europa League)
OL,9,Fand we're getting further and further
OL,10,Finto the competition," he said.
OL,12,F"It's been hard to focus on our
OL,13,FPremier League form. So now we've done
OL,14,Fwhat we set out to do. We've achieved
OL,15,FChampions League football and now
OL,16,Fwe're going do all we can to win on
OL,17,FWednesday.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@VO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
