CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779034270
OL,3,COllie Watkins seeks inspiration from
OL,4,CPeter Withe's 1982 European Cup winner
OL,6,F"We were meant to do it in that
OL,7,Ffashion (on Friday night) and for it
OL,8,Fto be in the last home game as well
OL,9,Fmakes it even more special I think."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
